arch tome
name Flora's Domain
msg
Most of Flora's Domain is the large
jungle to the south of Yoer's kingdom.
Flora used to be an ally of Yoer's
kingdom before King Yoer disapeared.
There are two cities in Flora's
Domain,the City of the White Rose and
Flora City. The city of the White Rose
is said to have a magical white
rose,which contributes to the city's
prosperity. Flora City is Flora's
capital.
There is also a large cave in the
southern part of the jungle. It is
called the Cave of Vines. Little else
is known about Flora's Domain.
endmsg
