arch tome
name Darkland:volume 3
msg
To the north of Glovarit and Rithar is
Lavaland. Lavaland is a hot,fiery land
filled with lava and volcanos. Rumor
has it that a important city lies in
Lavaland.
Southeast in darkland is the Gnomish
village. To the North is a dark
forest filled with savage trolls and
orges. Most of the denizens of darkland
worship evil gods such as
Ruggilly,Devourers,and Gnarg.
End..
endmsg
