name Yoer's Kingdom
msg
The Land of Yoer is a elf ruled country.
The Elves in that kingdom are generally
light elves. The original king of that
land dissapeared years ago. His son now
rules for him.
Yoer City is known for its many
advances and wonders. Some of its
wonders are Yoer Stadium,the Royal
Cathedral,the Royal Palace,the Royal
Library,and its large University.
To the west of Yoer is Fleabeon. A
small town ruled by Fleabolt. Fleabeon
was founded by King Fleabeon. Fleabolt
is Fleabeon's grandson.
endmsg
